PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-574 of April 15, 1997, respecting the appointment of GORDON WHITEHEAD to the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), by revoking the words "part-time member" and substituting the words "full-time member".
